explanation: [0-0] Six lit yellow candles are placed in a metal container under a hydraulic press. Both the container below and the hydraulic press above have yellow and black colors. There are many holes on the metal disk of the hydraulic press.

[0-4] The press slowly descends, deforming the candles inside. As the hydraulic press continues to descend, the candle wax is pushed outward and upward, turning into many long yellow strips that spray out.
